      <description>The Reboot Your Life diet has both fans and skeptics. The program comes on the heels of Joe Cross&amp;#8217; 60 day juice fast, where he lost 100 pounds. Cross documented it all in a movie, &amp;#8220;Fat, Sick and Nearly Dead.&amp;#8221; Now those who want to take what Cross learned on the road and bring it [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/juice-cleanse/Juice_Cleanse-Reboot_Your_Life_Diet.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B002S51RRA/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=juicecleansenow-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B002S51RRA"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1667" title="Reboot Your Life Diet Uses Breville Juicers" src="http://www.juicecleansenow.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/Screen-shot-2011-08-04-at-8.59.17-PM.png" alt="Reboot Your Life Diet" width="243" height="294" /></a>The Reboot Your Life diet has both fans and skeptics. The program comes on the heels of Joe Cross&#8217; 60 day juice fast, where he lost 100 pounds. Cross documented it all in a movie, &#8220;<a title="Read our &quot;Fat, Sick &amp; Nearly Dead&quot; review" href="http://www.juicecleansenow.com/juice-fast/fat-sick-nearly-dead-movie-review/">Fat, Sick and Nearly Dead</a>.&#8221;</p>
<p>Now those who want to take what Cross learned on the road and bring it inot their own homes can do so with the Reboot Your Life website and it&#8217;s associated juice cleansing and juice fasting plans.</p>
<p>With the Reboot Your Life program, you take an assessment of your current health, weight, commitment level and goals and a program is recommended for you. You&#8217;re given a week to prepare for your program and then you receive emails each day with a full meal plan for the day ahead. It didn&#8217;t work for me, because I&#8217;d get the messages in the morning and often wouldn&#8217;t have the specific ingredients for the juice recipes on hand. Thankfully, I&#8217;ve got a bunch of great <a href="http://www.juicecleansenow.com/juice-cleanse-books/">juice cleanse books on hand (here are my top 3)</a> to find a substitute.</p>
<div id="attachment_1670" class="wp-caption alignright" style="width: 310px"><a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B002S51RRA/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=juicecleansenow-20&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B002S51RRA"><img class="size-medium wp-image-1670" title="See the Breville juicers the Reboot program uses" src="http://www.juicecleansenow.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/Screen-shot-2011-08-04-at-8.59.01-PM-300x296.png" alt="Reboot Your Life Diet" width="300" height="296" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">The Reboot your Life Diet uses Breville juicers like this one - click to read reviews.</p></div>
<p>Reboot juice fasting might not be juice fasting at all, in that you may be given a program that includes eating fresh fruits and vegetables in the raw, depending on your answers to the initial quiz. For this reason, it has received some criticism for not being &#8220;pure&#8221; to juce fasting.</p>
<p>That being said, I think it&#8217;s a good thing when the barriers to entry are lowered for better health. I&#8217;d much rather see folks eating more fruits and vegetables over not making any changes to their diets at all, right?!</p>
<p>Aside from the encouraging daily emails (with the recipes that weren&#8217;t a good fit for me), the Reboot Your Life program has a massive community supporting each other, which can be helpful to newbie juicers just getting started.</p>
