      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>There are different ways to cleanse your body, if you want fast and sure way to cleanse your body; you only need to use the 3-day Juice Cleanse. This is one way of cleansing and detoxing your body by eliminating the harmful toxins inside your body. It could help you in losing your weight, get rid of cellulite and bloating, it can also increase your energy levels.</p>
<p>The 3-day Juice Cleanse only requires taking fresh vegetable and fruit juice mixture and limiting the intake of your regular meals. This will help you lose your sugar craving, balance your hormones, get clearer skin and eyes, stops feeling unhealthy, tired and sluggish and you could also gain mental clarity. This 3-day dieting program doesn?t have any harmful effects in your body.</p>
