      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.juicecleansenow.com/?p=580</guid>
      <description>Juice fasting and detoxification is a short term program that uses juice as a main ingredient to minimize or totally dissolve unwanted fats. Because juice fasting and detoxification uses juice, it is a source of good vitamins and minerals that could nourish our body. There are different reasons why people juice fast. Some of them [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/juice-cleanse/Juice_Cleanse-A_10-Day_Miracle_of_Juice_Detox.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Juice fasting and detoxification is a short term program that uses juice as a main ingredient to minimize or totally dissolve unwanted fats. Because juice fasting and detoxification uses juice, it is a source of good vitamins and minerals that could nourish our body.</p>
<p>There are different reasons why people juice fast. Some of them include religious reasons, losing weight and attempting to wean one from unhealthy habits, i.e., smoking, drinking soda, overeating, and caffeine addiction. However, it is not advisable to be in this program while pregnant or if the person has diabetes and low blood pressure.?It cleanses the colon and changes the metabolism. It typically last for about two weeks or ten days. It can also clears skin making it look fresher and even toned.</p>
<p>Though several users proven its effectiveness, still, there are some critics that disapprove this kind of detoxifying. But there is really no harm in trying and seeing the result why more people are discovering their true self with this miracle juice detox.</p>
